data.description: Nestled within the pristine Copperstone gated community in Parrish, this 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem exudes elegance from the moment you arrive. The home's curb appeal is a testament to its refined character, setting the stage for a remarkable living experience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting interior. The heart of the home boasts a large kitchen featuring sleek granite countertops and beautifully crafted wood cabinets. The addition of a convenient bar countertop adds a touch of sophistication and makes this space perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. The home's high ceilings create a sense of openness and grandeur, enhancing the open floor plan that offers limitless possibilities for various activities. Throughout the house, you'll find a tasteful combination of ceramic tile and gorgeous wood flooring, which adds warmth and character to the living spaces. One of the standout features of this property is its serene and private setting. With no neighbors across the street, you'll enjoy an unobstructed view that overlooks a pond. This captivating view can be admired from both the living room and the sliding glass doors, allowing you to connect with nature and enjoy the tranquil beauty of the surroundings. Adding to the home's appeal is a solar system, a modern touch that not only reduces your carbon footprint but also contributes to energy efficiency and cost savings. Copperstone itself is a well-maintained community, offering residents access to a range of amenities. A clubhouse and community pool are just some of the perks that enhance the quality of life for those fortunate enough to call this community home. With its ideal location, exquisite features, and the peaceful serenity of its surroundings, this property in Copperstone presents an opportunity to experience luxurious living in a welcoming and vibrant community.
